START: Hostel-Register
    Get a student's enrollment number and read the input.
    Convert the input enrollment number to uppercase.
    Split the input enrollment number into degree, year, and number.
    Format the enrollment number.
    IF the enrollment number exists in the database (checked using the check_enrollment function):
        Get a destination and read the input.
        Get the current time.
        Add a record to the database using the add_record function.
        Print a success message and continue the loop.
    ELSE print an error message and continue the loop.